/>\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uqYMQ6G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuqYMQ6G.png&h=b5266f40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n魚生算幾有質素，一定好過爭鮮啲垃圾，啲蝦好甜，池魚三文魚都鮮甜，我唔特別好魚生，都覺得好滿意。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YPmeZZ2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYPmeZZ2.png&h=b128619f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我鍾意食壽司多過魚生，呢個花之戀好正，細細舊一口一件，飯少魚生多蟹子夠，好食又唔會太飽肚，正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/21pHprK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F21pHprK.png&h=ac5ec15b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n火炙蟹棒，三文魚腩，三文魚壽司，細細件，好食又唔會太飽肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 🍣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t9v7Ayy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft9v7Ayy.png&h=0f4d8e7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n炸生蠔同炸雞翼，香脆可口，裹面雞肉仲係幾嫩滑，蠔亦有蠔汁，食得出係即炸，唔錯！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CxkSMFe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCxkSMFe.png&h=1357ea64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n芝士蒜蓉焗扇具，呢個個味幾香口，不過啲扇具肉<br />\n有啲乾，唔太特別。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/27jDHdA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F27jDHdA.png&h=d5b06c23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今次黎呢間食嘅重點，任點燒鰻魚！<br />\n唔多講啦，唔好客氣，食到就叫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢轉連埋第二轉，我食左7舊，出去食<br />\n個7，80蚊嘅鰻魚飯都未必有咁多鰻魚你食🤤<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZjzwhMW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZjzwhMW.png&h=42d96556&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蒜香炒牛肉粒，牛肉香口美味，唔會太硬又有啲「趙」口，送酒一流！可惜我唔多飲酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V3YpCMX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV3YpCMX.png&h=ce3a3fe2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另一樣食放題嘅比較貴食材，香草燒羊架，都幾好食，不過有啲硬，應該唔係即燒，似炸香再返燒個面，係幾香羊肉味，鍾意食嘅巴絲可以多食幾舊。<br />\n<br />\n第二轉再order 左呢啲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/imemver/sUFn8TO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fimemver%2FsUFn8TO.png&h=32b317bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G2xhXM9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG2xhXM9.png&h=bcbf535e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n甜品拎左少少黎食，普通到不行，不吃也罷。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/80YMQ7M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F80YMQ7M.png&h=a5c5a84f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雪糕無貴價野，主要都係牛奶公司各種雪糕杯同雪條，比較特別係👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻呢支榴槤雪條，cheap cheap地叫有啲榴槤香味，我個人幾鍾意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mPrOj07.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmPrOj07.png&h=f0b38888&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n總體而言，啲食物料質相當唔錯！而且全程無漏單<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係無漏單，呢點一定要讚！<br />\n啲侍應雖然好忙，不都都算有求必應，有禮貌，係令人滿意嘅。<br />\n1位，埋單196，無花無假，我單拖去食左放題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MsHNAKg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMsHNAKg.png&h=9c9e8027&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真你老母"},{"pid":"feb4450a93a8df118e7bdf8d4c67d9eba3c5b027","tid":951232,"uid":22736,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T07:44:31.000Z","msg":"百九蚊低食喎"},{"pid":"1a708a4c65f64043b3044a70da2fca3dc0de49af","tid":951232,"uid":12628,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"feb4450a93a8df118e7bdf8d4c67d9eba3c5b027","tid":951232,"uid":22736,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T07:44:31.000Z","msg":"百九蚊低食喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T07:50:39.000Z","msg":"真係低，2舊水，食元氣想食飽都未必得。"},{"pid":"7c5b6d6fd4b7df07561a64815d036d7869eda71c","tid":951232,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a708a4c65f64043b3044a70da2fca3dc0de49af","tid":951232,"uid":12628,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"feb4450a93a8df118e7bdf8d4c67d9eba3c5b027","tid":951232,"uid":22736,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T07:44:31.000Z","msg":"百九蚊低食喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T07:50:39.000Z","msg":"真係低，2舊水，食元氣想食飽都未必得。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T08:05:34.000Z","msg":"中午價？"},{"pid":"da7775fa0fbbed901dde2a116006928869f7caf1","tid":951232,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c5b6d6fd4b7df07561a64815d036d7869eda71c","tid":951232,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a708a4c65f64043b3044a70da2fca3dc0de49af","tid":951232,"uid":12628,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"feb4450a93a8df118e7bdf8d4c67d9eba3c5b027","tid":951232,"uid":22736,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T07:44:31.000Z","msg":"百九蚊低食喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T07:50:39.000Z","msg":"真係低，2舊水，食元氣想食飽都未必得。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T08:05:34.000Z","msg":"中午價？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T08:08:33.000Z","msg":"係，夜晚應該要2百幾"},{"pid":"febeb9c9f05eb4c459e7c8bbfb0c7972cd75f937","tid":951232,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T09:08:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c28c5029199bc4e1c721f1cabf89df19cea180","tid":951232,"uid":38765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T10:11:29.000Z","msg":"有睇你嗰個po<br />\n終於找數<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真漢子<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e416ee78fc1f8eca8c3c04908d02538cac4b0c5f","tid":951232,"uid":165479,"like":6,"dislike":34,"score":-28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-